snippet.title: Golf Peaks - Nintendo Switch launch trailer ESRB
snippet.description:
Golf Peaks - out now on Nintendo eShop! 

No understanding of golf is required – just grab your controllers and conquer the mountain peaks by making your way to the hole, however not in the usual skill-shot based style. Instead, plan your strategy and use action cards to move the ball!

Available now on Nintendo Switch! https://www.nintendo.com/games/detail/golf-peaks-switch

#NintendoSwitch #GolfPeaks

See more at:
